description: The interviewee could never have imagined what he was letting himself in for when he turned up at Miss de Lacy's office. As an unusual way of separating the wheat from the chaff, she indulges in a humiliation exercise for her unsuspecting new candidate. This includes a vicious tongue lashing, spitting, foot slapping, sweaty foot worship, trampling and smothering him in a variety of creative and humiliating ways.
title: The Interview
